Alrighty.

420
00:24:05,119 --> 00:24:06,319
Please take your feet down.

421
00:24:06,319 --> 00:24:08,319
I got it, I got it. I got it, I got it.

422
00:24:12,720 --> 00:24:13,400
Cover up a little.

423
00:24:13,400 --> 00:24:16,119
I'm fine, I want to be discharged.

424
00:24:16,119 --> 00:24:17,319
Let's listen to the doctor.

425
00:24:17,440 --> 00:24:18,880
We'll leave whenever the doctor says we can.

426
00:24:18,880 --> 00:24:20,000
That's when we'll be discharged.

427
00:24:20,359 --> 00:24:21,400
Don't rush.

428
00:24:21,400 --> 00:24:22,680
