431
00:24:25,079 --> 00:24:26,640
Go and get it done for me right now.

432
00:24:26,839 --> 00:24:28,599
I said, don't rush, don't rush.

433
00:24:28,599 --> 00:24:30,160
What, are you afraid he'll run off?

434
00:24:30,160 --> 00:24:31,119
Don't you rush.

435
00:24:32,720 --> 00:24:33,599
I want to be discharged.

436
00:24:33,599 --> 00:24:35,400
