Didn't we agree?

842
00:40:46,480 --> 00:40:47,800
To have two children.

843
00:40:47,920 --> 00:40:50,079
We'll definitely need my parents to help.

844
00:40:50,760 --> 00:40:52,480
And your father isn't in good health either.

845
00:40:52,840 --> 00:40:55,000
So he'd have to live with us too.

846
00:40:55,239 --> 00:40:56,400
This current place...

847
00:40:59,039 --> 00:41:01,159
...really isn't big enough.

848
00:41:02,320 --> 00:41:04,280
Your parents, my parents,

849
00:41:04,280 --> 00:41:05,880
us two, plus the kids...

850
00:41:07,159 --> 00:41:09,000
This apartment is a bit small.

851
00:41:09,880 --> 00:41:11,000
But look, how about...

852
00:41:11,000 --> 00:41:13,079
...we put this apartment

853
00:41:13,079 --> 00:41:14,199
on the market and sell it first?

854
00:41:14,199 --> 00:41:16,480
Then we can find a bigger place.

855
00:41:16,480 --> 00:41:17,800
We'll pay the down payment,

856
00:41:17,800 --> 00:41:20,440
and figure out the rest of the money later.

857
00:41:20,800 --> 00:41:22,320
But you're saying because of this,

858
00:41:22,320 --> 00:41:23,360
you... you're going to Xi'an?

859
00:41:23,360 --> 00:41:25,480
I... I think that's too hard on you.

860
00:41:26,440 --> 00:41:28,199
It's fine, really, it's fine.

861
00:41:28,519 --> 00:41:30,239
If I become a director,

862
00:41:30,760 --> 00:41:32,280
a little hardship won't matter.

863
00:41:32,679 --> 00:41:34,679
That way, you won't have to worry about promotions.

864
00:41:34,679 --> 00:41:36,199
The extra time...

865
00:41:36,360 --> 00:41:38,199
...could be used to take care of our dad, right?

866
00:41:38,320 --> 00:41:40,000
Do I have to spell it out for you?

867
00:41:40,000 --> 00:41:41,360
I can't bear to be apart from you.

868
00:41:42,360 --> 00:41:44,199
I can't bear to be apart from you either.

869
00:41:45,039 --> 00:41:46,039
So what you're saying is,

870
00:41:46,039 --> 00:41:47,840
if we had a big house right now,

871
00:41:48,119 --> 00:41:49,960
you wouldn't go to Xi'an, right?

872
00:41:54,719 --> 00:41:56,320
Where would such a good thing come from?

873
00:41:56,320 --> 00:41:57,559
You're dreaming.

874
00:42:00,920 --> 00:42:02,119
Not bad, huh? This idea.
